{"tid":1336393,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"明天維園見：不送頭，不死守","createTime":"2019-07-21T02:52:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T02:56:07.000Z","uid":267783,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f16944dde365959ace0dc8fcd4229a666092ae5b","tid":1336393,"uid":267783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T02:52:35.000Z","msg":"梁啓智：<br />\n和很多朋友一樣，我對明天的情況十分擔憂。警察對民陣的要求，明顯是要增加而不是要減低遊行的風險。我不是鄺神，沒什麼資格呼籲前線怎樣做。但我想，這場運動既然每個人都有份，那我就以一個參與者的身分在此給予一個微小的意見：不送頭，不死守，可以嗎？警察濫權，大家都看得見，不用更多的犧牲來證明。要增加專制的管治成本，還有很多其他方法。如果明天不幸有任何衝突的話，希望大家可以主動互相提點：齊上齊落，我們還要一起迎接勝利。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zxXsyr3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzxXsyr3.png&h=7270736e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/594642803906393/posts/2301763943194262?s=1140112797&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F594642803906393%2Fposts%2F2301763943194262%3Fs%3D1140112797%26sfns%3Dmo&d=3A6Iqvk0VBPdaidkhJ82W7ktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=58023bf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/594642803906393/posts/2301763943194262?s=1140112797&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"05bf3ffd71cf2aa0dfd9cb85415df933c5a08de0","tid":1336393,"uid":201512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T02:56:07.000Z","msg":"唔好再起roadblock!"}]}